<br>
If you are late then the RL may award you fewer RP. Most are fairly leniant and won't do anything if you're 15 minutes late or so, but if you join half way through then you can't really expect to get full RP.<br>
<br>
I often sign up for raids and state that I might be late due to having to get home from work. If I can join the raid I will, but I wouldn't expect anyone to come to pick me up - this can be a problem in Kael Arena as most people can't make their own way past the see-invis line. I think its preferable to sign up with a "maybe" than to not sign up and just turn up on the day.<br>
<br>
All in all though its up to the raid leader and there are no fixed rules regarding these matters. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=271048"><b>Goldark Stormwind</b></a><br>Shaman Prophet<br>
